  <title>Scores</title>

  <p>You can view your scores for all the games played for every puzzle.</p>
    <steps>
      <item><p>Select <guiseq><gui style="menu">Gnome-klotski</gui>
      <gui style="menuitem">Scores</gui></guiseq>.</p></item>
      <item><p>You can select a puzzle from the drop down menu and view all
      the number of moves you took with the date when you played it by
      scrolling through it.</p></item>
      <item><p>Click on <gui style="button">Ok</gui> to close the scores menu.
      </p></item>
    </steps>
